The directory conf/ is used for initial installation of nginx (mirror.conf file)

The directory /scripts is used for local syncronization (make sync) and remote deployment (make deploy)

'root' file is the crontab-file for process scheduling

Dockerfile is used for building the image (we copied the files 'mirror.conf' and 'script.sh' into nginx directory)

Makefile is used to do some jobs (syncronization - make sync, deployment - make deploy) 

